_sText:
ze_surf_legoland_c2

Map Info:
Map contains
8 Surf Levels.
3 Defend Points.
2 Stages.
2 Bosses. ( Evil Steve & Forever Knight).
Some good music.
Lasers ( Stage-II) Only.

Description
I originally intended the map to consist of 3 stages with 3rd stage being the longest one but I simply got lazy considering this is my last map. That's why map contains no items and can be doable without them. I will update the map in the future maybe.. if requested, i.e add items, make Stage-III.But for the mean time, this will be my final map. Explore the cursed land of lego, and find your way to defeat the notorious entity. GL & HF.

! Map may contain bugs. If you find any. Let me know :)
